    {
      "id": "PopularPost327079",
      "post_content": "Once [Hellrider](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hellrider) rotates, this thing will become the best red curve-topper in Standard. Until then, it might see fringe play in midrange decks that don't expect to win by turn 4. I love the power he brings. This effect was previously seen on [In the Web of War](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=In the Web of War), another card I am a big fan of. For best results, use with tokens. Both halves of [Lingering Souls](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lingering Souls) swings for 12 in the air on turn 5.",
      "posted_by": "Avensai",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost327079\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Once <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hellrider\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hellrider\">Hellrider</a> rotates, this thing will become the best red curve-topper in Standard. Until then, it might see fringe play in midrange decks that don't expect to win by turn 4. I love the power he brings. This effect was previously seen on <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"In the Web of War\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=In the Web of War\">In the Web of War</a>, another card I am a big fan of. For best results, use with tokens. Both halves of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lingering Souls\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lingering Souls\">Lingering Souls</a> swings for 12 in the air on turn 5.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '327079'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy88185\">Avensai</span>\r\n                                (7/10/2013 12:54:37 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRat