    {
      "id": "PopularPost327636",
      "post_content": "I'm not normally good at calling out cards I believe will make a major impact on Standard.  \nHowever, I didn't call [Hellrider](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hellrider) when I shoulda, and I feel that this guy in the same league as him.  \nSo, here it is, I'm going to say that this card will make a pretty solid impact in Standard.",
      "posted_by": "infernox10",
